IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. EvaluateTest.

DATA DIVISION.
01 age picture is 99.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
EVALUATE age
    WHEN 18
        DISPLAY "Adult"
    WHEN 13 THROUGH 17
        DISPLAY "Teen"
    WHEN OTHER
        DISPLAY "Child"
END

EVALUATE 1 + 2 * 3
    WHEN age < 18 AND age > 12
        DISPLAY "True"
END.
